sections.label: Key Technologies
sections.value: TypeScript, Vue.js, Angular, Node.js, Kotlin, Spring Boot

sections.label: Responsibilities
sections.value:
Developed, enhanced, and maintained multiple web applications. Coordinated and communicated
in cross-project/cross-team environments. Planned and estimated upcoming work, providing detailed assessments. Traced and debugged production issues across applications. Designed and implemented a dynamic form mapping solution for objects with embedded structures. Led a team to standardize front-end settings and styles, ensuring a cohesive user experience across applications.

sections.label: Responsibilities
sections.value:
Developed and maintained back-end services, including REST and SOAP APIs, enhancing system
performance and reliability. Skillfully debugged and resolved issues within internal applications, contributing to improved stability and user experience. Successfully created a React-based interface, integrated with a Google Chrome extension, to augment browser functionality. Additionally, spearheaded the refactoring of core web service functionality, optimizing code efficiency and maintainability.

sections.label: Responsibilities
sections.value:
Collaborated in the design and implementation of a solution using Java and Apache Wicket,
contributing to enhanced application functionality and user experience. Provided support in developing and maintaining REST Services, aiding in system integration and data exchange. Applied strong debugging skills to identify and resolve complex issues, ensuring optimal system performance and reliability.
